modules.description: Generates and verifies bcrypt hashes with built-in salting, ensuring secure password storage. Operates on string inputs for passwords and encoded hash strings for verification. Used in web applications to protect user credentials during registration and login processes.

Provides functions to hash passwords with automatic salting using Bcrypt, verify passwords against stored hashes, and convert between strings and hash values. Operates on strings, hash values, and a variant type specifying Bcrypt algorithm versions. Used to securely store and check user credentials in authentication systems.
